text: Change Your World is the second solo album of Hillsong Church's worship pastor, Darlene Zschech. ==Album details== Change Your World comprises twelve originally-recorded 'Christian pop' and worship songs. ==Track listing== # "You Are Here" (words: Darlene Zschech and Mia Fieldes; music: Zschech and David Holmes) – 5:09 # "Miracle" (words and music: Zschech and Holmes) – 5:20 # "Captured" (words: Zschech and Kathy Sorenson; music: Zschech and Holmes) – 4:25 # "Call Upon His Name" (words and music: Zschech) – 3:39 # "You Know My Name" (words: Zschech; music: Holmes) – 3:53 # "Never Give Up" (words and music: Zschech and Holmes) – 3:29 # "Change Your World" (words: Zschech; music: Zschech and Holmes) – 6:08 # "Where Would I Be" (words: Zschech; music: Zschech and Holmes) – 4:39 # "Glorify Your Name" (words and music: Zschech and Holmes) – 5:16 # "Sing Over Me" (words: Zschech; music: Zschech and Holmes) – 5:01 # "You Are Holy" (words: Zschech; music: Zschech and Holmes) – 4:45 # "Agnus Dei" (words and music: Michael W. Smith) – 5:34 ==See also== * Extravagant Worship: The Songs of Darlene Zschech * Kiss of Heaven ==External links== *Darlene Zschech's home page Category:2005 albums
